<!--T:7-->
# Optionally specify the line attributes with the [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes|TechDraw ExtensionSelectLineAttributes]] tool.
# Select the first vertex to determine the center point of the arc.
# Select the second vertex to determine the radius and the start angle of the arc.
# Select the third vertex to determine the end angle of the arc.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionDrawCosmArc.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionDrawCosmArc|Add Cosmetic Arc]]}} button.
